  __awaiter(void 0, void 0, void 0, function* () {
    yield jest_setup_1.aui.typeIn("www.app.askui.com").textfield().exec();
    yield jest_setup_1.aui.pressKey("enter").exec();
    yield jest_setup_1.aui
      .typeIn("janosch.jenson@yopmail.com")
      .textfield()
      .contains()
      .text("Email address")

    yield jest_setup_1.aui

      .textfield()
      .contains()
      .text("Password")
      .exec();
    yield jest_setup_1.aui.click().button().withText("Continue").exec();
    yield jest_setup_1.aui.click().text("Access Tokens").exec();
    yield jest_setup_1.aui
      .click()
      .table()
      .col(3)
      .leftOf(0)
      .text("Jenkins")
      .below(1)
      .text("Name")
      .exec();
    yield jest_setup_1.aui.click().text("YES, DELETE").exec();
  });
